(Corrects Suntech’s forecasts for shipments this year and
third-quarter results in Nov. 12 summary of an Economy & Nation
Weekly report after the magazine corrected the figures.)  “Suntech isn’t on the edge of
bankruptcy,” Vice President Gong Xuejin said, according to a
report dated Nov. 8 in The Economy & Nation Weekly, a magazine
controlled by the Xinhua News Agency.  To contact the reporter on this story:
